        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "I think the linked SO answer is more about writing `except +` handlers to override Cython's own default exception handling.\n\nI've recently added some template trickery which should make it a little easier (https://cython.readthedocs.io/en/latest/src/userguide/wrapping_CPlusPlus.html#cython-3-3) because it gives you access to the exception instance from Cython.",
